summary: Intelligent, creative, and committed scientific project leader. I'm driven by my main values integrity, transparency, responsibility, and engagement. As I remain close to my values, I notice my style is much appreciated and I tend to get things done. As project leader, I continue to be surprised by the big steps a well organized and motivated team can make.  I'm most energized when I serve as 'spider in the web' and subject matter expert, taking the  lead, advocate for my people and projects, all to turn common ambitions into shared success.
